{"_path":"/maps/_business/low-code","_dir":"_business","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"低码","description":"","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"低码"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"低码"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"todo"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TODO"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/361233277","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"低代码平台设计的边界问题"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://juejin.cn/post/6918881497264947207","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可视化拖拽组件库一些技术要点原理分析"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"项目参考"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"项目参考"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"使用-mybricks-搭建计算器"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使用 MyBricks 搭建计算器"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"简介"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"简介"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"什么是低码"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"什么是低码？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"低代码是指使用可视化技术来创建应用的平台，特点是应用中的代码量要比传统开发少得多。低码是一种理念，许多商业产品在十几甚至几十年前就开始尝试用 GUI 的方式来开发应用了，只是在今年来才改名叫低码平台。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"模式"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"模式"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"react-框架下改变组件父级会导致组件-remount-怎么解决"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"React 框架下改变组件父级会导致组件 remount 怎么解决？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可以使用 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/1fYO__dfUy2MIjHi3IJrmg","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"KeepAlive"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 模式解决。在画布的 DOM 结构中用 KeepElement 作为组件的 DOM 包装，而组件本身通过 createPortal 的方式挂载到画布外的地方。这样一来，和拖拽相关的 KeepElement 结构而言组件层级是正确的，对于渲染相关的结构而言，父子结构没有改变，所以不会触发组件的 remount。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"todo","depth":2,"text":"TODO"},{"id":"项目参考","depth":2,"text":"项目参考"},{"id":"简介","depth":2,"text":"简介"},{"id":"模式","depth":2,"text":"模式"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_business:low-code.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_business/low-code.md","_extension":"md"}